yang bercita-cita untuk jadi penyanyi."

242
00:18:37,846 --> 00:18:41,016
Siapa yang awak maksudkan? Tentulah saya.

243
00:18:41,725 --> 00:18:43,894
Awak memang petah bercakap.

244
00:18:43,977 --> 00:18:45,437
Kalau petah sangat,

245
00:18:45,520 --> 00:18:47,773
kenapa diam saja
ketika mereka ambil duit awak?

246
00:18:47,856 --> 00:18:49,650
Nasib baik Ha-young datang.

247
00:18:49,733 --> 00:18:51,777
- Hei, itu rahsia.
- Siapa dia?

248
00:18:51,860 --> 00:18:54,071
Beritahu saya. Saya akan balas dendam.

249
00:18:54,154 --> 00:18:55,572
Mereka tak ambil.

250
00:18:55,656 --> 00:18:57,908
Lagipun, mereka minta sikit saja.

251
00:18:57,991 --> 00:18:59,451
Sejak bila mereka buat begitu?

252
00:19:08,168 --> 00:19:09,711
Waktu di sekolah menengah,

253
00:19:11,296 --> 00:19:13,215
mereka kurung saya di dalam stor

254
00:19:14,633 --> 00:19:17,636
dan ugut saya
dengan menyuruh saya menyanyi.

255
00:19:18,845 --> 00:19:21,014
Tapi kerana sangat takut…

256
00:19:22,349 --> 00:19:24,059
- saya…
- Awak terkencing?

257
00:19:28,981 --> 00:19:31,942
Sejak itu, mereka gunakan itu
untuk buli saya.

258
00:19:33,443 --> 00:19:34,653
Memalukan, bukan?

259
00:19:35,862 --> 00:19:37,072
Jangan mengarut.

260
00:19:37,155 --> 00:19:39,324
Kali pertama belajar berenang,

261
00:19:39,408 --> 00:19:42,619
saya buang air kecil dalam kolam renang.

262
00:19:47,457 --> 00:19:49,251
Saya dipulaukan di sekolah menengah.

263
00:20:01,221 --> 00:20:02,389
Waktu kecil,

264
00:20:02,973 --> 00:20:05,142
saya pernah mabuk kerana
terminum wain plum.

265
00:20:05,225 --> 00:20:06,935
- Biar betul?
- Biar betul?

266
00:20:07,519 --> 00:20:08,812
Bila? Di mana?

267
00:20:09,563 --> 00:20:10,647
Awak tak perlu tahu.

268
00:20:14,151 --> 00:20:16,611
Ayah pernah dijangkiti
kaki makan air kerana saya.

269
00:20:16,695 --> 00:20:18,864
Awak serius?

270
00:20:18,947 --> 00:20:20,240
Ini mengejutkan.

271
00:20:20,324 --> 00:20:22,659
Bukankah ini hal kecil saja?

272
00:20:23,577 --> 00:20:25,245
- Saya tak rasa begitu.
- Apa?

273
00:20:26,371 --> 00:20:28,206
Stoking awak hari itu…

274
00:20:28,874 --> 00:20:31,543
Taklah. Saya dah sembuh.

275
00:20:31,626 --> 00:20:33,337
Dah sembuh sepenuhnya.

276
00:20:33,920 --> 00:20:34,921
Cik Shin Sol-i.

277
00:20:35,005 --> 00:20:37,466
Penyakit kaki makan air boleh kembali.

278
00:20:40,135 --> 00:20:42,262
Jin-hwan! Saya benci awak!

279
00:20:42,346 --> 00:20:44,348
Ha-young, tolonglah saya!

280
00:20:44,431 --> 00:20:46,433
Sudah. Berhenti sekarang juga.

281
00:20:47,559 --> 00:20:49,770
- Berhenti mengusik.
- Betul!

282
00:20:49,853 --> 00:20:51,355
Awak pakai stoking apa?

283
00:20:56,443 --> 00:20:59,696
1999, KEDIAMAN SOL-I

284
00:20:59,780 --> 00:21:01,323
Tepis.

285
00:21:02,115 --> 00:21:03,033
Serang!

286
00:21:03,116 --> 00:21:05,911
Tepis dan serang!

287
00:21:05,994 --> 00:21:08,246
Teknik apa yang awak tunjukkan ini?

288
00:21:08,330 --> 00:21:09,873
Awak minum semua itu?

289
00:21:09,956 --> 00:21:12,000
- Heon, awak okey?
- Aduhai.

290
00:21:12,918 --> 00:21:16,380
Tangan kanan, tangan kiri.

291
00:21:17,547 --> 00:21:20,592
Tepis dengan tangan kanan.

292
00:21:23,470 --> 00:21:24,805
Aduhai.

293
00:21:25,639 --> 00:21:28,225
Dia pasti akan berjaya satu hari nanti.

294
00:21:28,308 --> 00:21:30,268
Aduhai.

295
00:21:30,852 --> 00:21:32,187
Comel betul.

296
00:21:50,831 --> 00:21:52,874
<i>Heon, awak boleh jadi penyanyi.</i>

297
00:21:52,958 --> 00:21:54,543
Nah, guna ini.

298
00:21:54,626 --> 00:21:56,002
<i>- Awak okey?</i>
- Terima kasih.

299
00:21:56,086 --> 00:21:59,089
<i>- Di negara lain dah ada kematian.
- Saya akan mati?</i>

300
00:21:59,172 --> 00:22:00,882
<i>Jangan risau. Awak okey.</i>

301
00:22:00,966 --> 00:22:02,801
<i>Heon, awak tak lawat Sol-i?</i>

302
00:22:02,884 --> 00:22:04,428
Di mana Heon?

303
00:22:04,511 --> 00:22:05,887
<i>Tolong serahkan untuk saya.</i>

304
00:22:05,971 --> 00:22:07,514
<i>Ini daripada Cha Heon.</i>

305
00:22:07,597 --> 00:22:09,349
<i>Siapa yang timbulkan masalah?</i>

306
00:22:09,433 --> 00:22:12,686
<i>Saya harap saya akan sakit lagi.</i>

307
00:22:12,769 --> 00:22:15,021
<i>Sol-i, jangan risau.</i>

308
00:22:16,148 --> 00:22:21,153
Terjemahan sari kata oleh Hazizah Ali

